		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Wondrous Item - Uncommon</p><p><em>This deceptive dust looks identical to @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.equipment24.Item.dmgDustOfDisappe]{Dust of Disappearance}, but it seizes the lungs of nearby creatures.</em></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 30 ft Emanation (Self)</p><p>Take a Utilize action to hurl the dust into the air. You and every creature within 30 feet of you must attempt a DC 15 Constitution saving throw; Constructs, Elementals, Oozes, Plants, and Undead automatically succeed.</p><p><strong>[[/save CON 15]]{Constitution Save (DC 15)}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The creature starts violently sneezing, becoming Incapacitated and beginning to suffocate.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Properties</strong></p><ul><li><p>An affected creature repeats the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.</p></li><li><p>The effect ends early if the creature receives a <em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells24.Item.phbsplLesserRest]{Lesser Restoration}</em> spell.</p></li><li><p>The dust is consumed when used.</p></li></ul>",
